{"type":"message","id":"513a5d2a","parentId":"ee4831ac","timestamp":"2026-04-16T15:06:57.026Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-16 23:06:55 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9 [msg:om_x100b513bfe282cacc113daf59f20f14]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b513bfe282cacc113daf59f20f14\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-16 23:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\"\n}\n```\n\n深度研究superpowers，输出一份15000字左右的技术博客文章，深度剖析所有skills的提示词，以及工作流程，输出到https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/JqLawtcbHiYqrskD6EBc2ZmvnXg文档下"}],"timestamp":1776352017022}}
{"type":"message","id":"55193a7a","parentId":"513a5d2a","timestamp":"2026-04-16T15:07:06.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to deeply research \"superpowers\" (which likely refers to the OpenClaw skills system) and write a ~15000 word technical blog article analyzing all skills' prompts and workflows, outputting to a Feishu wiki document.\n\nLet me start by:\n1. Reading the skills directory to understand all available skills\n2. Reading each skill's SKILL.md\n3. Understanding the overall architecture\n4. Writing the comprehensive article\n\nLet me first explore the skills directory structure.","thinkingSignature":"da06818417e576c5b7417464668348109b31e0ea8b1e386bd1a2d859f4bfcce3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o8hw7uew3jay_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw -name \"SKILL.md\" | head -50 && echo \"---\" && find ~/.openclaw/shared-skills -maxdepth 2 -type d | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":149,"output":165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":37341,"totalTokens":37655,"cost":{"input":0.00008939999999999999,"output":0.000396,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.014002875,"total":0.014488275}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776352017023}}
{"type":"message","id":"4e48a653","parentId":"55193a7a","timestamp":"2026-04-16T15:07:06.479Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o8hw7uew3jay_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/admin/.openclaw/workspace/skills/feishu-send-image/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/workspace/skills/humanizer/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/workspace/skills/mcporter/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-troubleshoot/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-bitable/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-calendar/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-fetch-doc/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-create-doc/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-update-doc/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-task/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-im-read/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-channel-rules/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/feishu-send-image/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/skill-vetter/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/ontology/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/t2i/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/find-skills/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/self-improving/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/feishu-wiki-write/SKILL.md\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/proactive-agent/SKILL.md\n---\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/feishu-send-image\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/skill-vetter\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/skill-vetter/.clawhub\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/ontology\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/ontology/scripts\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/ontology/references\n/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-s