{"type":"message","id":"bf897c6b","parentId":"a01e08f7","timestamp":"2026-04-16T15:11:26.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The document was created successfully. Let me also update the wiki node to put it in the right place. Let me provide a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"dbf65b34a60a0c09c36422d461766227da43e8cf46855a8952247320c7b8580f"},{"type":"text","text":"文章已成功写入飞书知识库！\n\n**📄 文档信息**\n- **标题**：OpenClaw Skills 深度剖析：架构、工作流与最佳实践\n- **链接**：https://www.feishu.cn/wiki/OzzewPH44igpVQkZ4C9cgn6xnbf\n- **Doc ID**：`N9UOdDSFwoT8CTx8NV1cB1UTnAc`\n\n---\n\n**📊 文章概览（约15000字）**\n\n全文共分为九个章节，系统覆盖了 OpenClaw 部署的全部 Skills：\n\n**第一部分 - 飞书集成类（11个技能）**\n- feishu-im-read：话题展开策略 + 图片下载链路设计\n- feishu-calendar：user_open_id 隐性必填哲学 + 会议室异步预约\n- feishu-task：completed_at 三义语义 + 清单角色冲突\n- feishu-bitable：27种字段值格式 + 超链接字段最反直觉坑 + 空行污染问题\n- feishu-fetch-doc：Wiki Token 三步解析流程\n- feishu-create-doc：Lark-flavored Markdown 完整语法（含 Mermaid/Callout/Grid 等）\n- feishu-update-doc：7种更新模式的精确语义与安全边界\n- feishu-troubleshoot：智能诊断协议\n- feishu-channel-rules：alwaysActive 输出规范\n\n**第二部分 - AI增强类（3个技能）**\n- humanizer：24类AI味检测模式 + Before/After 改写范例\n- self-improving：HOT/WARM/COLD三层记忆 + 自动提升降级规则\n- proactive-agent：WAL Protocol + Compaction Recovery + ADL/VFM进化协议\n\n**第三部分 - 工具型（5个技能）**\n- t2i：中文提示词优化流水线\n- find-skills：技能发现引擎 + CLI命令体系\n- mcporter：MCP服务器直连设计\n- skill-vetter：五层信任审查 + 立即拒绝红旗清单\n- ontology：知识图谱 + 类型约束引擎\n\n**第四部分 - 系统级（2个技能）**\n- healthcheck：八步安全强化流程 + 四种风险画像\n- skill-creator：三层渐进披露设计 + 六步创作流程\n\n**第五部分 - 总结**\n- 四种知识形态分类\n- 触发机制设计艺术\n- 按需加载的上下文管理\n- 工作流原子化设计\n- 错误码作为知识载体"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":71473,"output":561,"cacheRead":37026,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109060,"cost":{"input":0.0428838,"output":0.0013464,"cacheRead":0.0022215599999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.046451759999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776352270464}}
